---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Devender Gollapally">
  <div class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 12px;">
    <p class="kicker">About</p>
    <h1>Devender Gollapally</h1>
  </div>

  <section style="max-width: 680px;">
    <p>
      I'm a Principal Software Engineer who has spent two decades building systems that move
      real money: investment platforms, secondary markets, escrow and custody integrations, and
      most recently production <strong>agentic AI</strong> in regulated finance.
    </p>

    <p>Some things I've built or helped build:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong><a href="https://github.com/ethereum/ERCs">ERC-1450</a></strong> — co-author of
        the Ethereum standard for transfer-agent-controlled security tokens; over
        <strong>$1B in securities</strong> has been tokenized on this pattern.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong><a href="https://mcpwright.com">mcpwright</a></strong> — a suite of open-source
        MCP servers that put public data inside AI agents:
        <a href="https://mcpwright.com/edgar">SEC EDGAR</a> and
        <a href="https://mcpwright.com/census">U.S. Census</a>, with more coming. Typed, tested,
        one-click installable in Claude Desktop.
      </li>
      <li>
        Production LLM systems for compliance and operations — the unglamorous, high-stakes kind
        where the model's work gets reviewed by regulators, not just users.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      I've been writing here since <strong>2003</strong> — the archive runs from Hibernate and
      Spring through Ruby, Clojure, Redis, and Neo4j to today's agents. I leave the old posts
      up: they're an honest record of what building software has looked like for twenty years.
    </p>

    <p>
      Away from the keyboard: fountain pens, a ukulele, and a steady stack of books — I keep a
      running list of <a href="/reading/">what I read</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="muted">
      Elsewhere: <a href="https://github.com/devender">GitHub</a> ·
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/devender">LinkedIn</a> ·
      <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/30218868-devender-gollapally">Goodreads</a> ·
      <a href="https://mcpwright.com">mcpwright.com</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
